name: 2009-round-economically-active-population-projections
title: 2009 round economically active population projections
description: Projections produced are consistent with both published sets of population projection. The first of these incorporated development trajectories derived from the 2009 Strategic Housing Land Availability Assessment and the second is based on the development trajectories assumed for the London Plan.

resources.name: gla-ecoactive-2009rnd-shlaa-borough.xls
resources.description: Economically active population projections to 2031 for London boroughs.  These projections are consistent with the 2009 round SHLAA-based population projections.

resources.name: gla-ecoactive-2009rnd-londonplan-borough.xls
resources.description: Economically active population projections to 2031 for London boroughs.  These projections are consistent with the 2009 round London Plan-based population projections.
